{"data":{"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"AI-based Remote Proctoring System","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/56208/rp.png","srcSet":"/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/659f7/rp.png 175w,\n/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/19d7e/rp.png 350w,\n/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/56208/rp.png 700w,\n/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/57bcc/rp.png 1400w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/368a3/rp.avif 175w,\n/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/930de/rp.avif 350w,\n/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/c567c/rp.avif 700w,\n/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/3d5be/rp.avif 1400w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/fb9f4/rp.webp 175w,\n/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/ac70d/rp.webp 350w,\n/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/c53fa/rp.webp 700w,\n/static/be28ce7d232142e4e4af459eb884fd7f/0acfd/rp.webp 1400w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":419}}},"tech":["Python API","OpenCV","Java","MySQL"],"github":null,"external":null,"cta":null},"html":"<p>Developed and integrated the Candidate Exam Procturing System with the Candidate Test Player using Computer vision techniques to monitor the live candidates.</p>\n<!-- ---\ndate: '1'\ntitle: 'Halcyon Theme'\ncover: './halcyon.png'\ngithub: 'https://github.com/bchiang7/halcyon-site'\nexternal: 'https://halcyon-theme.netlify.com/'\ntech:\n  - VS Code\n  - Sublime Text\n  - Atom\n  - iTerm2\n  - Hyper\n---\n\nA minimal, dark blue theme for VS Code, Sublime Text, Atom, iTerm, and more. Available on [Visual Studio Marketplace](https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=brittanychiang.halcyon-vscode), [Package Control](https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Halcyon%20Theme), [Atom Package Manager](https://atom.io/themes/halcyon-syntax), and [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/package/hyper-halcyon-theme). -->"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"BMS - Electric Vehicle","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/0e84cddbb62df3d1b413ac2be828c8db/16a35/GUI.png","srcSet":"/static/0e84cddbb62df3d1b413ac2be828c8db/9a130/GUI.png 175w,\n/static/0e84cddbb62df3d1b413ac2be828c8db/a3fa1/GUI.png 350w,\n/static/0e84cddbb62df3d1b413ac2be828c8db/16a35/GUI.png 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/0e84cddbb62df3d1b413ac2be828c8db/dae43/GUI.avif 175w,\n/static/0e84cddbb62df3d1b413ac2be828c8db/d7667/GUI.avif 350w,\n/static/0e84cddbb62df3d1b413ac2be828c8db/fa1f8/GUI.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/0e84cddbb62df3d1b413ac2be828c8db/5d873/GUI.webp 175w,\n/static/0e84cddbb62df3d1b413ac2be828c8db/26a00/GUI.webp 350w,\n/static/0e84cddbb62df3d1b413ac2be828c8db/81f83/GUI.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":393}}},"tech":["C++","GTK+","Controller Area Network"],"github":null,"external":"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9008088","cta":null},"html":"<p>A custom Battery Management System was designed and developed end to end. This involves the pcb designing, cell data logging and telemetry. The system/cells data is wirelessly transferred using a CAN protocol to a PC using BeagleBone black processor where a real time GUI using GTK+ dashboard is created to display all the cell statistics and their criticality statuses. The work was later extended to predict the State of Charge (SoC) with the help of neural networks.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Reinforcement Learning-Atari Games","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/6d8ab/qlearning.png","srcSet":"/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/a15a6/qlearning.png 175w,\n/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/15da0/qlearning.png 350w,\n/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/6d8ab/qlearning.png 700w,\n/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/aada5/qlearning.png 1400w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/96e31/qlearning.avif 175w,\n/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/8024a/qlearning.avif 350w,\n/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/564a2/qlearning.avif 700w,\n/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/ca5cf/qlearning.avif 1400w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/37045/qlearning.webp 175w,\n/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/3d0d8/qlearning.webp 350w,\n/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/0ffb2/qlearning.webp 700w,\n/static/27710cf23b852f01f47769e2070e2220/25514/qlearning.webp 1400w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":370}}},"tech":["Python API","Gym","TensorFlow"],"github":null,"external":null,"cta":"https://www.google.com"},"html":"<p>Implemented and compared the performances of various Reinforcement Learning Techniques like Q-learning, DQN, etc on various Atari Games like breakout, pong, etc.</p>\n<!-- Also, transferring the knowledge from parent game to child game. -->\n <!-- Later, optimized the network to perform better than than initial one.  -->"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"World Map - Candidate Status","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/3d8ed4235bff78a4808a6affa28ec183/a115a/WorldMap.png","srcSet":"/static/3d8ed4235bff78a4808a6affa28ec183/3a042/WorldMap.png 175w,\n/static/3d8ed4235bff78a4808a6affa28ec183/90d1f/WorldMap.png 350w,\n/static/3d8ed4235bff78a4808a6affa28ec183/a115a/WorldMap.png 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/3d8ed4235bff78a4808a6affa28ec183/ab4e6/WorldMap.avif 175w,\n/static/3d8ed4235bff78a4808a6affa28ec183/024b9/WorldMap.avif 350w,\n/static/3d8ed4235bff78a4808a6affa28ec183/ab5c3/WorldMap.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/3d8ed4235bff78a4808a6affa28ec183/32753/WorldMap.webp 175w,\n/static/3d8ed4235bff78a4808a6affa28ec183/ab163/WorldMap.webp 350w,\n/static/3d8ed4235bff78a4808a6affa28ec183/c2d65/WorldMap.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":342}}},"tech":["Java","SQL","HTML"],"github":null,"external":null,"cta":null},"html":"<p>Based on the statistics of the candidates scheduled, attended, ongoing, and completed tests, a dynamic live dashboard showing the candidates' numbers for each country was shown. The live data of the test takers in a certain country is shown as the mouse is over that nation. From the db batch and candidate tables, a one to many mapping is done to fetch the data of the number of the candidate status in a specific batch every minute using a cron job.</p>\n<!-- Displaying a dynamic live dashboard of the candidates count on a world map for every country based on the statistic of the candidates Scheduled, Attended, Test In Progress & Test Completed. As the mouse hovers over a specific country, the live data taking the exam in that country is displayed. The data is fetched regularly for the data base tables which gets updated for every 2 min cron job.  -->"}}]}}}